{"tid":1423482,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日小四女仔同我講咗個笑話(1Q題)","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:50:27.000Z","uid":4092,"like":87,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"363aad35031f73a4efabed751572254f1267861b","tid":1423482,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"我今日去幫個小四女仔補習<br />\n佢話同我講個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢: 你知唔知 policeman 中文係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我: (本身想答狗) 不過算啦 我答佢警察 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢: 錯喇！係暴力市民！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗返起細個都有講過依個笑話 但當時只係覺得搞下笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到今日竟然成真<br />\n<br />\n點都好 希望大家可以撐落去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"70367aab333f00204e32861930df45a0438287a4","tid":1423482,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88fe5b58799879acb795d805af6173eb41015ba","tid":1423482,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"2268aab891918e09dfad9370285feb17b17344b6","tid":1423482,"uid":138804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"已經笑唔出<img src=\"/ass